metadata.description: Stickman collectables is a collection of 10,000 randomly assembled Stickmen, it's home to a wide variety of personalities, Each Stickman is made up of a unique combination of eyes, mouths, heads and Backgrounds to match your vibe. Our Collection is community-driven, holding a Stickman allows you to take part in coordinating the Club's treasury, development and direction. Join us to be a part of our journey building something special.
